Amber Heard Plans On Getting Johnny Depp Lawsuit DISMISSED | The Gossipy

Welcome toThe Gossipy. We make interesting videos about Hollywood in English. We give you a closer look in the lives of celebrities like Kanye West, Ed Sheeran, The Rock, Jay Z, Selena Gomez, Kylie Jenner, Kim Kardashian, Rihanna and 100s more.

It has already been quite a bit of time since there was new evidence found in regard to the legal battle between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. Since the body cam footage was discovered, people all over were wondering just how Amber Heard was going to try and recover from the whole situation. 

Initially, once the body cam footage was shared everywhere Amber Heard did not seem to have much to say about it all, so could it be that even though the original court date got pushed back, that Amber Heard is trying to find another way out of it to save herself?
